  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A cestus is an armored glove which can be tightly tied around a hand, requiring an action to don or doff. While you can hold objects in a hand that wears a cestus, due to the cumbersome nature of the cestus you are unable to wield shields or other weapons in that hand. However, because of the way it is strapped on, you do not drop the cestus and cannot be disarmed of it unless someone takes an remove it from you while you are incapacitated.</p>\n<p>If you are proficient with martial weapons, the damage increases from 1d4 to 1d6 and you can grapple enemies with a hand that wields a cestus (though you can't attack with it while you grapple someone in that hand).</p>",
